--

$y = \frac{4}{5} x$


--
$1 = \frac{4}{5}x$


--
$x=\frac{5}{4} \text{ hour}$



---


iii) Use a constant of proportionality (unit rate) to determine how long it will take the scholar to complete the assignment. 


 $\frac{1}{2}$ hour per $\frac{2}{5}$ assignment


--
$\downarrow \times \frac{5}{2} \hspace{2.25em} \downarrow \times \frac{5}{2}$


